description: The Project 2013 SDK download includes the source files that are generated by the SvcUtil.exe command for the proxy assembly. The source files are in the Source.zip file in the Documentation\IntelliSense\WCF subdirectory. Instead of setting a reference to the proxy assembly, you can add one or more of the source files to a Visual Studio solution. For example, to use the Project service and the Resource service, add the wcf.Project.cs and wcf.Resource.cs files to the solution.
